8年出品)<br />\n好慚愧我係未睇過The Thin Red Line，而Dunkirk我下晝先睇<br />\n但我見你咁大口氣，所以想請教下你意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好過。"},{"pid":"33960a10248ddb3012b4f7c6d7c75b74a46598af","tid":329011,"uid":124450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:22:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好過The Thin Red Line？(一套被Nolan奉為神作的電影，1998年出品)<br />\n好慚愧我係未睇過The Thin Red Line，而Dunkirk我下晝先睇<br />\n但我見你咁大口氣，所以想請教下你意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好過。</blockquote><br />\nTerence Malick同Christopher Nolan冇可比性<br />\n一個係電影藝術家 一個係商業奇才"},{"pid":"4a978aae578258297509050e0408cbc9a8b8af37","tid":329011,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T06:43:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c07d9fffa5df1aec363b3f144a7625bb375f19d","tid":329011,"uid":82331,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T07:00:38.000Z","msg":"唔算戰爭片，但認同係今年神作"},{"pid":"5773bba8b2281703ba9e36d250a2bc9847cdcee6","tid":329011,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T07:07:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔算戰爭片，但認同係今年神作</blockquote><br />\nTDK唔叫英雄片。Dunkirk唔叫戰爭片。"},{"pid":"699bce352d95f6e544604f7acb5e89983aac7ecd","tid":329011,"uid":57723,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T07:08:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔算戰爭片，但認同係今年神作</blockquote><br />\nTDK唔叫英雄片。Dunkirk唔叫戰爭片。</blockquote><br />\n袁木好誠實，李鵬係我地最偉大嘅領袖"},{"pid":"d57ef79c4d1886c2f256072f69330dc8997a6dcc","tid":329011,"uid":82331,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T07:11:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔算戰爭片，但認同係今年神作</blockquote><br />\nTDK唔叫英雄片。Dunkirk唔叫戰爭片。</blockquote><br />\n都無戰爭場面，純粹諗計走佬炸"},{"pid":"7e3b07836152456e46e1a670af842d18d99af54c","tid":329011,"uid":113516,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T07:12:39.000Z","msg":"今朝睇完，唔係好覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反而係有少少失望"},{"pid":"39bd1a02b4e6df2ce82e4910859abab20539de7e","tid":329011,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T07:12:51.000Z","msg":"聽晚睇<br />\n上YouTube睇咗啲外國影評，講係非一般戰爭片嘅拍法，好期待"},{"pid":"0aea2c65298045369bb6eeffb219cbda85411911","tid":329011,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T07:28:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc70c85cfe66860e79d051019dffe67eb063165","tid":329011,"uid":113516,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T09:01:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽晚睇<br />\n上YouTube睇咗啲外國影評，講係非一般戰爭片嘅拍法，好期待</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實係似救生片多<br />\n中間個timeline我覺得有d亂<br />\n報紙話Tom Hardy 得10句對白但我數過唔只10句咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61dcb6d77bb88cdf55bdcf105e0c5997cde777ac","tid":329011,"uid":102096,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T09:01:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a329a57a10a1c949450330bfb817e0154d47ea9","tid":329011,"uid":34029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T09:04:01.000Z","msg":"飛已買一陣出去睇"},{"pid":"8d59994ebe40f6f63de962379405ca0d5537df5a","tid":329011,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T09:13:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e5ccbafd30962da024d91a99799f6ccf8ab28b7","tid":329011,"uid":113516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T09:31:35.000Z","msg":"好想同你地瘋狂討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我今朝突登去睇9點早場，應該係全港最早既第一場"},{"pid":"00486a9e6e33fb209be4985149a8e71b5c2c1028","tid":329011,"uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T09:35:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好想同你地瘋狂討論<img src=\"/asset