片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e304d943e5da621c3b34749bbb5ca86719027892","tid":329011,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T12:56:39.000Z","msg":"點解會話saving係好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"157e1af4e27780cb8bd044712a6965f2c0e277be","tid":329011,"uid":42382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T20:48:56.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"cddbddc3826a983e6317101d5aedd60609b76c90","tid":329011,"uid":11185,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T23:27:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解會話saving係好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n1.美帝光環<br />\n真人真事改篇，美帝見人地家族死淨麥迪文一粒仔，可以派一隊人去捨身取義<br />\n完全彰顯美帝既人道精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2.場D-DAY登陸戰拍得好，場面夠大夠慘烈<br />\n<br />\n3.教材級現代戰爭片"},{"pid":"574798ae86d865140ae2ffc54a9bc3e57fac93db","tid":329011,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T05:43:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解會話saving係好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n1.美帝光環<br />\n真人真事改篇，美帝見人地家族死淨麥迪文一粒仔，可以派一隊人去捨身取義<br />\n完全彰顯美帝既人道精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2.場D-DAY登陸戰拍得好，場面夠大夠慘烈<br />\n<br />\n3.教材級現代戰爭片</blockquote><br />\n最重要係成套製作認真 聲音煙火(不同煙花)裝備效果好真實 近20年真實路線戰爭片都係由佢開先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6828d3eb5da18a3cef3deb4b8607c9d4d2af03a6","tid":329011,"uid":16491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T07:09:57.000Z","msg":"根本唔係戰爭片，而係懸疑片"},{"pid":"bf4fe963d2c1fd33c20e4f97548910338a6909aa","tid":329011,"uid":1391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T07:15:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本唔係戰爭片，而係懸疑片</blockquote><br />\n唔係懸疑片<br />\n我覺得Dunkirk好難分類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19e82a13950f692da19ec6839ef71e842b35646d","tid":329011,"uid":126247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T07:39:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Win 到 珍珠港 ？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n廿年最佳幾時輪到pearl harbour?<br />\n緊係the one and olny既saving private ryan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今晚睇 希望真係突破到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢講笑姐"},{"pid":"484a5c0e8bd29311d1ab6dbdae463eb4e4518e71","tid":329011,"uid":60341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T07:39:55.000Z","msg":"的確係非一般戰爭片<br />\n佢重點唔係慘烈嘅戰爭場面（當年英法聯軍dunkirk 防線打到仆街）<br />\n而係喺海灘/船上唔知幾時會被炸嘅不安感<br />\n所以上面有人同saving private ryan比係唔公道（所以套戲PG13都唔奇怪）<br />\n<br />\n今次"},{"pid":"3c9e2fec231f55504687e5794f02ecef94742590","tid":329011,"uid":90863,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T07:41:17.000Z","msg":"美國狙擊手都不如"},{"pid":"b2b441444ffb0ebb3c7d072a11fbd9570ef32f83","tid":329011,"uid":60341,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T07:43:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>的確係非一般戰爭片<br />\n佢重點唔係慘烈嘅戰爭場面（當年英法聯軍dunkirk 防線打到仆街）<br />\n而係喺海灘/船上唔知幾時會被炸嘅不安感<br />\n所以上面有人同saving private ryan比係唔公道（所以套戲PG13都唔奇怪）<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n今次nolan將四條唔同時間點嘅故事線一齊講，亦都同其他戰爭片有決定性上嘅分別<br />\n最後所有線sync返埋一齊做得好好"},{"pid":"71d33908e98de3de6534e4b7ac5746d9bcfa2145","tid":329011,"uid":63735,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T08:06:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好過The Thin Red Line？(一套被Nolan奉為神作的電影，1998年出品)<br />\n好慚愧我係未睇過The Thin Red Line，而Dunkirk我下晝先睇<br />\n但我見你咁大口氣，所以想請教下你意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個人覺得好唔過（雖然好難比較，始終劇本深度有別）<br />\nThin Red Line可以話係Malick作品中最能（亦可以話係唯一）體現到海德格哲學的一部<br />\n利申：幾憎Malick，唔係Christopher Nolan fans"},{"pid":"e8b89ea3a1214022164757848feb0c4e2aeeb3ef","tid":329011,"uid":56084,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T09:02:42.000Z","msg":"悶到on9 wo   成場一係就影d船 一係就飛機 一係就個beach... 都唔知自己睇緊乜"},{"pid":"493ce4abe6e0465f2976e10d68ea7bdf8205f6a1","tid":329011,"uid":4586,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T09:52:47.000Z","msg":"樓主廿年睇過幾多戲<br />\n唔好問我係咪on9 <br />\nsample size matters"},{"pid":"560909111dcdd388258195cefcb9aa33164591b0","tid":329011,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T09:55:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>贏到雷霆救兵？</blockquote><br />\n贏9條街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a30ed93e36880529e1ee99e4449438a5226cf1d9","tid":329011,"uid":43152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T09:58:25.000Z","msg":"我覺得nolan將戰爭片嘅拍法改寫左<br />\n用三條主線分插敍事好特別，故事選材都特別<br />\n以前所有點戰爭片都會張顯英雄主義，一個打十個，一條主線打到埋<br />\n但係今次個主線反而係要諗點走鬼，用生存同希望做主題，突顯左人係戰爭被動嘅一部分，人係打輸要生存個種醜惡自私，都係好入骨，唔同mochael bay個d一味爆粗爆炸屌到尾，哩套戲多左一種文藝feel,有種picture speaks a thousand words<br />\n少左對白，多左感受<br />\n個人好欣賞tom hardy 個結局，同埋三線合一個諗法真係世界級"},{"pid":"816f3d79a39318ffcbb20050ef41c6ccddafe9df","tid":329011,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T10:03:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>贏到雷霆救兵？</blockquote><br />\n贏9條街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb3f002751c6746e6cdc3c36f1933f832dd2b992","tid":329011,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-2